data.description: Adorable semi-detached home in the heart of Lititz! This home has 3 bedrooms, main floor laundry, a nice sized fenced in rear yard with large shed. Main floor living space is an open floor-plan and waiting for your creative touches to make it your forever home! You will enjoy the rear fully fenced large yard that is perfect for summer activities. All appliances stay with the home and quick possession is possible. This could be a great rental or keep it for yourself and enjoy living in the beautiful Lititz community within walking distance to great shopping, restaurants, walking paths and more!
